'''Card's Tapcaf''' was a small [[Tapcafe/Legends|tapcafe]] on [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]. It was still in existence at the time of the [[Second Galactic Civil War]] and was where [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] discussed with [[Dur Gejjen]] about the possibility of assassinating [[Thrackan Sal-Solo]].

Card's Tapcaf was located on [[Blue Sky Boulevard]] in the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Coronet City/Legends|Coronet]].

